Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爹 艾拉暫時拜託給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是等等後援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這條腿已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能截肢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會忘記和你一起工作過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我不會再和你搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感謝各位協助瑪莎的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然結果變成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過沒有把一般民眾捲入事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以說是不幸中的萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外關於地下回收業者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總公司通知說 已和R.Security社合作將其一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎麼說負責這個案件的司和艾拉並沒有過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在聽嗎 司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖說不是你們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但也必須負點責任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你在艾拉恢復出勤之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留在事務所待機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就這樣解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他堅持說要熬夜陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是個頑固的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天就可以活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過你的身體本來就有點毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還需要幾天時間來調整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會再和你搭檔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 現在幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是深夜 要睡的話還是回宿舍比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你沒事 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整整昏睡了兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大叔還對我吼說「維護期間不需要陪護 快出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總覺得有點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}萬一艾拉你就這樣一直醒不過來了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}瑪莎和湊太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月小姐他們在做後續處理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像全部由我們處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你 這樣關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒事的 真的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼 你還能笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽好哦 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為現在調整還沒有全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下班後不要回宿舍 要直接來這邊喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會全心全意照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 你沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}維護班說還需要繼續調整一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 麻煩泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總是麻煩你真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說司啊 你今天還是陪我去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會帶你去有很多漂亮姐姐的店裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用不用 之前也告訴過你我還未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝 不要一大早就說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下流下流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克可不要這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們課的女同事還是一樣不近情理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉難不成你看上我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次去約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 我沒有在看康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我脆弱的心剛才受到了深深的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 就算是安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陪我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小艾拉 茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文件都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和你分開來上班 總有種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為最近都是一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你笑起來很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突…突然這是怎麼了 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 司對你做了什麼奇怪的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心 我們會站在你這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯 我也聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢欺騙純情的艾拉拉 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,666,640,710,209,918)}看情況 有必要考慮把他從宿舍趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 艾拉拉 儘管說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點在意司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗚哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}注意到的時候 發現目光一直在追隨他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明之前沒有這麼在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 這就是所謂的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫做戀愛的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是戀愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 戀愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 應該不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是這樣 我會全力支持你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具體來說 我可以24小時監視小司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徹底掌握小司的生活狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生活狀態？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說你啊 這跟跟蹤狂差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要了解關於喜歡的人的一切 這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有經驗 所以很瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們明天就開始調查哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不會陪你們
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司到底在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該是我的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉同意他看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼做這麼大膽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他說想瞭解終端服務課的工作規定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是借給他看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看日記是最快的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉的一切都赤裸裸的寫在日記裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好羡慕啊 我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是小司司一邊看一邊壞笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要說噁心的話 繪瑠你也…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 總感覺有人在看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有可能是地下回收業者的殘黨在謀劃恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我們的辦公室？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果真的會幹那種事的話也是瞄著本部大樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉對偷窺的戒備可是很強的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你覺得是誰讓我變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道…是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉比香月可怕多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不會因為這點小事就放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繼續啊 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們繼續吧 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想再陪你們玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近女兒好像找到男朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不好呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小心點 那個很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來已經晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別光是笑 來幫我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你們再喝多點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在喝啊 雖然只是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不走我老婆要發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對呢 我知道了 你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 連去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道啊 可能去廁所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起這個 香月小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喝太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別給我指指點點的 司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到竟然要我陪她一起通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H7C6C72&\pos(638,314)}男子浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然在這碰到了 真巧啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是小司偶然在那裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是偶然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託了雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 你明明沒必要和繪瑠一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是她真的有非常努力地幫我想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你在意司的哪個方面呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才剛剛經歷過瑪莎的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不懂司為什麼還能保持笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}確實那傢伙一直都笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司不會是已經忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人有那種忘記不想記住的東西的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我從來沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道司現在是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前我和香月小姐一起去了湊太家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}準備和他說明一下瑪莎的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那之後發現司也在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙明明應該在事務所待命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卻一個人去找湊太道歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}瑪莎去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還沒能和瑪莎好好道別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你跟我說好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要把瑪莎帶回這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓我見見瑪莎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之後 他被香月小姐說「不要擅自行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被狠狠罵了一頓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他肯定也是沒辦法忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想他也不會讓自己忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那為什麼司會笑得出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 到底為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是因為悲傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿在溫柔的時候真的很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 艾拉 這話是什麼意思
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 這不是某部的部長嗎 真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老闆娘 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都到這裡了還工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是個無趣的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微和老闆娘說說話怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是應該對那些喧囂的店更加有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有時會路過這附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次的事 找R.Security社來干預的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是我也有我的辦事原則
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來職位高也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 今天到此為止 沒有什麼大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說明天就可以開始工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 今晚就可以回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受不了就說受不了就行了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是我一直在拖大家後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回到現場去工作真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不想回歸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是可能又會添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是麻煩 不是由你來決定 而是司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8870E7&\3c&HE9EBEC&\fs30\frz25.027\pos(244,416)}甜蜜新婚生活手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的剩餘時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有沒有從艾拉那裡聽到些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉因為和你搭檔改變了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和與我搭檔的時候樣子很不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟那時消耗非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也是因為她暫時休息了一陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓艾拉有所改變的 毫無疑問是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那樣的話 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}僅剩差不多1000小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 1000小時是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概一個月多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個月…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那時就要和對其他的吉芙提爾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必須對艾拉進行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我原本沒有打算瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是最後就拖到了這時候才說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我對此道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你打算怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是要就這樣繼續和艾拉搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是要解除與她的搭檔關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等待新的吉芙提爾分配過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算要繼續這樣搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎樣 一個月之後你和艾拉的搭檔關係都會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和艾拉一直搭檔到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在我無法想像和艾拉以外的人搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你確定要那樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對哦 今天開始你就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是去接你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎回來 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司也是 歡迎回來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一會兒是先吃飯 還是先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是 吃～我～呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 難道是繪瑠小姐教給你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 是從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8870E7&\3c&HE9EBEC&\fs30\frz341.217\move(994,709,994,381,0,400)\frx14\fry30}甜蜜新婚生活手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊～～～
